    effortless-ntwf:source "Synthetic dataset derived from Charig 1986 kidney stone rates but with equal treatment allocation across strata (175 cases per cell). Demonstrates that the reversal in the original study is purely an allocation artifact." ;
    effortless-ntwf:sourceUrl "" .

